  "body": "### Description\n\nCurrently for the kubernetes family of extensions `Knative` is treated as a platfrom similar to vanilla `Kubernetes` and `OpenShift`. \r\nHowever, this is not accurate as `Knative` could run on top of any platform.\r\n\r\nWe should explore the possiblility of making knative a deployment resource instead similar to `Deployment`, `StatefulSet`, `Job` etc. In this spirit we could have `Service` or `KnativeService` or `ksvc`.\n\n### Implementation ideas\n\n_No response_",
